  <meta name="citation_reference" content="Kshetri, N., Rahman, M. M., Sayeed, S. A., &amp; Sultana, I. (2023). cryptoRAN: A review on cryptojacking and ransomware attacks w.r.t. banking industry -- threats, challenges, &amp; problems. arXiv preprint arXiv:2311.14783.">
